24
00:03:11,110 --> 00:03:12,150
Where is he now?

25
00:03:15,330 --> 00:03:16,680
There's this handsome guy in a band

26
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,330
who invited me to go to his performance.

27
00:03:18,330 --> 00:03:19,980
