180
00:08:57,610 --> 00:08:58,840
You can use your paintings

181
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,740
as thematic elements.

182
00:08:59,740 --> 00:09:00,190
Right?

183
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,780
