193
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:29,010
The grapes in this vineyard have grown exceptionally well this year.

194
00:09:29,010 --> 00:09:30,370
Once we sell all the grapes

195
00:09:30,370 --> 00:09:31,680
from this vineyard,

196
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:33,020
