409
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:39,300
What's the matter?

410
00:18:39,300 --> 00:18:41,030
Don't want me to tell the truth?

411
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:44,040
Too bad. You want to pretend,

412
00:18:44,070 --> 00:18:46,230
