-What do you mean?
-Ms. Qin,

445
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:12,400
who is he?

446
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:13,700
Free child labor.

447
00:20:13,770 --> 00:20:15,640
I'm her brother. Her real brother.

448
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:16,100
Sister,

449
00:20:16,100 --> 00:20:18,160
