00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:36,600
Let's give "lazy" to Cheng.

489
00:21:37,220 --> 00:21:39,220
Why am I lazy?

490
00:21:39,250 --> 00:21:40,270
Are you indirectly

491
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:42,130
